data.description: 3/4 Acre Estate in West Miami-Dade County on private cul-de-sac.  Plenty of room to add a pool, Concrete slab ready for RV and several boats.  Porte-cochere entrance. High ceilings, Formal living and dining area.  Large kitchen with breakfast area opens to gigantic family room. Spacious home with great layout.  All bedrooms on one side. Primary suite is huge with 2 walk in closets, large bathroom with tub and shower. Covered terrace at rear extends length of the home. Accordion shutters for hurricane protection, fully fenced yard. Update this home and make it your own. Zone "X", not a flood zone.  No HOA.  A rare find, suitable for a large family with penty of room to grow.
